{"tid":454412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所好落後！芝加哥商業交易所第4季推出比特幣期貨！","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T06:00:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcfd4e05ac3b3879bfce4b85449e302a673b446","tid":454412,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362403-20171101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362403-20171101.htm&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=aecd656d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362403-20171101.htm&h=3c34fb82\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362403-20171101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1362403_1_20171101105436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1362403_1_20171101105436.jpg&h=253719b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n芝加哥商業交易所（CME）宣布，計劃第4季推出比特幣期貨，目前正等待監管審核。交易所方面表示，考慮到客戶對不斷發展的加密貨幣市場興趣愈來愈大，決定推出比特幣期貨合約。<br />\n<br />\n計劃推出的比特幣期貨合約將以現金結算，並以CME CF比特幣參考利率 （BRR） 為基礎，作為比特幣的美元「牌價」，每日更新一次。<br />\n<br />\n受到消息刺激，比特幣價格<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">突破6400美元，創歷史新高。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}